  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empowering 300 Refugee Women and Girls in Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project Creates an opportunity for Vocational Skills training and Sustainable Livelihoods for 300 Refugee single women and Teen mothers who are Household heads due to their refugee circumstances. RUFIT equips them with the skills to run Viable Income Generating Activities including a Savings and Loan activity to improve their Standards of Living. RUFIT will run Vocational skills training, Life skills training, entrepreneurship training and sensitisation of the beneficiaries on their rights.</narrative>
  </description>
